  <title>Gio.MENU_ATTRIBUTE_ICON</title>
  <p>The menu item attribute which holds the icon of the item.</p>  <p>The icon is stored in the format returned by <link xref="Gio.Icon.serialize"/>.</p>  <p>This attribute is intended only to represent 'noun' icons such as
favicons for a webpage, or application icons.  It should not be used
for 'verbs' (ie: stock icons).</p>
  <p>Since 2.38</p>
